MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Finding: F-002
Date: 2026-04-20
Figma node: 3235:5080
Property: button size
Expected: 40×40 (24px icon + 8px padding)
Actual: 10×10 (h-10 w-10; project tailwind config maps `10` → 10px)
Severity: High
File: src/components/TopNav.tsx:15

Reasoning: tailwind.config.js defines spacing.10 = "10px" (not 40px), so
h-10 w-10 rendered a 10×10 container and the 20×14 svg overflowed it.
h-40 w-40 resolves to 40×40 per the same config.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 src/components/TopNav.tsx | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/src/components/TopNav.tsx b/src/components/TopNav.tsx
index 0b72ec2..fc85774 100644
--- a/src/components/TopNav.tsx
+++ b/src/components/TopNav.tsx
@@ -12,7 +12,7 @@ export default function TopNav() {
     >
       <button
         aria-label="Open menu"
-        className="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center text-heading"
+        className="flex h-40 w-40 items-center justify-center text-heading"
       >
         <svg width="20" height="14" viewBox="0 0 20 14" fill="none" aria-hidden>
           <rect y="0" width="20" height="2" rx="1" fill="currentColor" />
